===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally a {{liushu|p|nocap=y}} of a fish spine. {{zh-l|*肉}} was added later to distinguish it. The top component corrupted into {{zh-l|*𠦬}}, making it a {{Han compound|ls=psc|朿|肉|c1=p|c2=s|t2=flesh|nocap=y}}.

